Definition: fulfilling the grammatical role of one of its constituents
Example: when `three blind mice' serves as a noun it is an endocentric construction
Synonyms: EXOCENTRIC, noun, cognition, grammar, c, fulfilling, the, grammatical, role, of, one, its, constituents, when, three, blind, mice, serves, as, a, it, is, an, endocentric, construction
Category: adj.all
